### تشغيل السيرفر أولاً: 
### php artisan serve

### 1. تحليل الفجوات والمهارات (Manual Text Example)
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/ai/cv/gap-analysis
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
    "target_job": "Flutter Developer",
    "manual_text": "I am a fresh graduate with a degree in Computer Science. I know basic C++ and Java. I have no experience in mobile development yet."
}

### 2. توليد خطة التعلم واقتراح الكورسات
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/ai/career/roadmap
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
    "target_job": "Flutter Developer",
    "missing_skills": ["Dart Programming", "Flutter Widgets", "State Management (Provider/Riverpod)", "API Integration in Flutter"]
}

### 3. توليد الكويز
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/ai/career/quiz
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
    "skills_to_test": ["Dart Programming", "Flutter Widgets"]
}

### 4. توليد السيرة الذاتية (ATS)
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/ai/cv/generate
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
    "user_data_text": "I am a fresh graduate with a degree in Computer Science. I know basic C++ and Java.",
    "new_skills": ["Dart Programming", "Flutter Widgets", "State Management (Provider/Riverpod)", "API Integration in Flutter"]
}
